		"name": "inovents - API Collection",
		"description": "### Welcome to the inovents API Collection\n\nThis collection contains all the endpoints needed to interact with the Event Ticketing System. \n\n### Setup\n1.  **Base URL**: Set a variable `BASE_URL` to your server's root (e.g., `http://localhost:3000`).\n2.  **Authentication**: Most endpoints require a JWT token. After logging in, copy the `token` from the response and set it as a variable named `TOKEN`.\n3.  **Variables**: The collection uses `{{BASE_URL}}` and `{{TOKEN}}` throughout.\n\n### Modules\n- **Auth**: Registration and user access.\n- **Events**: Discovery and management (Organizers).\n- **Bookings**: Ticket purchasing (Attendees).\n- **Tickets**: Digital ticket retrieval and entry validation.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
